    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo describes a Blocks Extensible Exchange Protocol (BEEP) profile that allows a BEEP peer to serve as an application-layer proxy.  It allows authorized users to access services through a firewall.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
